# Test Design Standards

Generate:

### Positive Cases

Valid user actions.

### Negative Cases

Invalid input.

### Boundary Cases

Minimum and maximum values.

### Exception Cases

System error scenarios.

### Permission Cases

Role-based access.

### Security Cases

Input validation.

